{"tid":1689918,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"抗警暴東屋台重開 街坊排長龍","createTime":"2019-11-03T05:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T16:34:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d943277ed103cbe2f73c6071ab7ef20ee07aaf26","tid":1689918,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:18:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191103/6LNYGSRGHAFJP4U44HXYKJ2LPI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191103%2F6LNYGSRGHAFJP4U44HXYKJ2LPI%2F&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpNUqyFx8t7fe88%2BQEXu6%2F%2FM%3D&h=6733d6ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191103%2F6LNYGSRGHAFJP4U44HXYKJ2LPI%2F&h=8658cc23\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191103/6LNYGSRGHAFJP4U44HXYKJ2LPI/</a><br />\n<br />\n抗警暴東屋台重開 街坊排長龍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】屯門日本食店東屋台老闆娘與胞弟上周三因拒絕警員硬闖店內搜捕抗爭者，被防暴警粗暴拉出店外按地拘捕，兩人涉嫌阻差辦公獲准保釋後，該店昨日終重開營業，但兩姊弟未有返回店舖，大批市民則專程到店光顧以示支持，門外大排長龍。不少街坊直斥警方無法無天，認為要大力支持同類良心店，更在店外貼滿心意字句，有留言指「老闆、老闆娘要平安，一定日日幫襯你」。<br />\n<br />\n位於良德街8號的東屋台事發後休業兩天，至昨中午12時終重開。早上11時半店舖未開門，門外已有一批市民排隊等候，之後顧客絡繹不絕，中午時分店外一度有近50名街坊大排長龍。據知老闆娘和胞弟獲釋後留在家中休息，暫時不會返回店舖，店舖另一名負責人魏先生昨再次感謝大家支持，並指昨日只能提供外賣，不設堂食。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/iMB0XFqTFe59JEoLjooXowQwVBg=/802x455/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/Q5MMSOVDGTLNPEQECFLMD6TOHA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FiMB0XFqTFe59JEoLjooXowQwVBg%3D%2F802x455%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FQ5MMSOVDGTLNPEQECFLMD6TOHA.gif&h=6cb65107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東屋台休業兩日後重開，大批市民蜂擁前往「懲罰」。張家豪攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「支持良心店 叫最貴嗰樣」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：保時捷播《榮光》警強拖司機落車㩒地押走<br />\n<br />\n到來光顧的王小姐家住屯門市中心，她表示過往甚少到良德街光顧食肆，但今次「要支持良心小店，叫最貴嗰樣嘢食」。她講述當晚看直播目睹警員的拘捕行動，直斥警方無法無天。另一名市民傅小姐帶同祖母前來支持，她說：「黃店唔多，要盡自己能力，幫得幾多就幾多。」她對當晚警方闖店舖拘捕感到憤怒，「呢度係私人地方，即使冇做過咩都拉」，認為警方越來越過份和猖狂，香港已稱不上再有法治可言。<br />\n<br />\n排隊的黃先生專程由大埔到來光顧，他指香港人必須支持良心店，涉事老闆娘是維護香港法治、自主，他到來支持只是小小心意。黃又說：「警察已經好過份，離晒譜。無論店舖內有咩人都好，警察都唔應該將店東拉出店外，按喺地下再綁住，之後衝入店內拉人都講唔通。」不少街坊亦在店外砌出連儂牆，貼滿表達心意的字句。有市民留言指「老闆娘，多謝你守護咗班街坊！好人一生平安」、「老闆老闆娘要平安，一定日日幫襯你」。<br />\n<br />\n上周三晚10時許，兩名男女於防暴警面前跳舞後走進東屋台，防暴警欲硬闖店內拘捕兩人，遭老闆娘與胞弟拒絕，警察即時失控粗暴將兩人拉出店外按地制服拘捕，之後再直入店內拘捕兩名食客。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張家豪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/jqWqO_ZLJqqtSlK8odNjZiTBJog=/802x249/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/MCCGZLVAFUBLMREJEOJUBUUD74.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FjqWqO_ZLJqqtSlK8odNjZiTBJog%3D%2F802x249%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FMCCGZLVAFUBLMREJEOJUBUUD74.gif&h=a064ca20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAppleDaily"},{"pid":"f50023ea759a3d845c8ea15a444933eeb17e2bd5","tid":1689918,"uid":262146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/daWoJsy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdaWoJsy.png&h=16518c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLQwSkW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLQwSkW.png&h=766c26b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLR4sUj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLR4sUj.png&h=1dd0aacc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nShare:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/454004001340790/posts/3162303350510828?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F454004001340790%2Fposts%2F3162303350510828%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpNUqyFx8t7fe88%2BQEXu6%2F%2FM%3D&h=1b8865f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/454004001340790/posts/3162303350510828?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\nRT:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/effygrande1/status/1190670210027552768?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Feffygrande1%2Fstatus%2F1190670210027552768%3Fs%3D21&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpNUqyFx8t7fe88%2BQEXu6%2F%2FM%3D&h=4537aab1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Feffygrande1%2Fstatus%2F1190670210027552768%3Fs%3D21&h=113297e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/effygrande1/status/1190670210027552768?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n死黑警從來無認真關心過香港人條命<br />\n講緊被死亡個案，佢仲係度冷笑、當笑話"},{"pid":"6a7c0238feca1886fd5b2c1f7c400ea89f963e67","tid":1689918,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:25:52.000Z","msg":"黃色民生圈係要幫襯其他黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25bfa1595d8d8be30c44dfcd097d1e8316633ca","tid":1689918,"uid":7331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:29:48.000Z","msg":"附近有間盤子工房係黃店<br />\n東屋台太多人既話去呢間排啦"},{"pid":"a9d37aa7b4fbbaaa0b226c7b842ec89da1114956","tid":1689918,"uid":149559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f30481bfcebeb2d63dcd92dfe2f94eb45af094","tid":1689918,"uid":149559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}